    "body": "Playback monitor now reads the OPPO's real /getglobalinfo flags (is_video_playing / is_audio_playing / is_bdmv_playing / is_disc_playing), confirmed live on an M9205 -- fixes the TV being reclaimed mid-playback. Fully preconfigured (OPPO 192.168.10.10, NFS nfs://192.168.10.20/srv/nfs/media -> /srv/nfs/media). Software-verified (21 tests); HTTP path + reachability confirmed on hardware. Install: Add-ons -> Install from zip -> service.oppokodibridge-2.0.4.zip"
  },
